    <string name="galaga_header_instruction">INSTRUCTION</string>
    <string name="galaga_content_instruction">
        • Slide to control the player plane.\n
        • Bullets fire automatically in Engineering Mode.\n
        • Defeat waves of Bees and avoid collisions.\n
        • Toggle shot styles in Settings to optimize combat.
    </string>

    <string name="galaga_header_tech_stack">TECHNICAL STACK</string>
    <string name="galaga_content_tech_stack">
        • Framework: Android Jetpack (Activity, Fragment)\n
        • Architecture: MVVM with Strategy Pattern\n
        • Data Handling: View Binding &amp; Data Binding\n
        • State Management: SingleLiveEvent (Lifecycle-aware)\n
        • UI Components: Material 3 Design System\n
        • Core Engine: Custom Game Loop with Vector Physics
    </string>

